{"tid":522544,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手問］點控制貓貓食糧份量？","createTime":"2018-01-07T16:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T07:26:13.000Z","uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ff43167d600f6895f4c45b38ba9b6648b729aabf","tid":522544,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"貓貓1歲幾，放緊長糧...<br />\n醫生話要佢控制下食糧既份量/次數，<br />\n想問下點樣分餐比佢食好？<br />\n咩時間？<br />\n分幾多餐？<br />\n份量大約幾多？<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8337adec3646f7f9a3a6246b737560dca453a73","tid":522544,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"貓唔太清楚, 但我隻狗就分早晚畀佢食<br />\n至於份量, 通常包糧個包裝袋會印有營養成分, 幾重嘅寵物, 一日或者一餐就要食幾多杯/克, 我餵早晚就將個數除二"},{"pid":"01384cf75f48f42ad46053069a76a9077b941e03","tid":522544,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"同埋我隻貓，佢只係食乾糧<br />\n零食個d咩都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪要比下濕糧佢食？"},{"pid":"d55fe7d18814e0dc7c68edc534d84520ba880692","tid":522544,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01384cf75f48f42ad46053069a76a9077b941e03","tid":522544,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"同埋我隻貓，佢只係食乾糧<br />\n零食個d咩都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪要比下濕糧佢食？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"睇你咩乾糧囉<br />\n<br />\n有D乾糧全肉 其實真係可以唔洗比濕"},{"pid":"f504aca40ff5f398f31c0069432d607f586231f3","tid":522544,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"我果隻長擺糧<br />\n佢鐘意就食幾啖<br />\n同埋我出門/食晚餐果時又倒糧同幾粒零食過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b343cb9ce08d58bbb81eab978100ecfe3424dad","tid":522544,"uid":144631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"乾糧我長放<br />\n再加早晚濕糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d2e102f73fffa92a17f5c4368f6bf7a39c40c4","tid":522544,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:31:25.000Z","msg":"唔餵濕糧會易生腎石？"},{"pid":"f23b904c1c148bab2a7e77d78113c012154ee8ef","tid":522544,"uid":144631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d2e102f73fffa92a17f5c4368f6bf7a39c40c4","tid":522544,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:31:25.000Z","msg":"唔餵濕糧會易生腎石？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"其實都唔會<br />\n但要飲夠水<br />\n<br />\n濕糧好處係本身有水份<br />\n你仲可以加水落去溝<br />\n等佢可以飲多啲水"},{"pid":"c28b5ca17f405bc887d7d0520d7be2fd8d89bcc9","tid":522544,"uid":64930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"朝早一次，夜晚返黎一次"},{"pid":"2e6e7ac040b302d994029233664d86462cf1ae92","tid":522544,"uid":106783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b343cb9ce08d58bbb81eab978100ecfe3424dad","tid":522544,"uid":144631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"乾糧我長放<br />\n再加早晚濕糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"我都係放長糧，夜晚返去餵罐就好似已經食飽左咁食幾啖就走左去... 係咪長糧應該放少啲等佢夜晚食多啲罐？"},{"pid":"deb88c4000dcb2d14336c67c6dad21114315c6e7","tid":522544,"uid":12839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"長糧+一星期先食2，3次罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1486304c43e4fce608371894b8853fbb6491d179","tid":522544,"uid":144631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e6e7ac040b302d994029233664d86462cf1ae92","tid":522544,"uid":106783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b343cb9ce08d58bbb81eab978100ecfe3424dad","tid":522544,"uid":144631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"乾糧我長放<br />\n再加早晚濕糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"我都係放長糧，夜晚返去餵罐就好似已經食飽左咁食幾啖就走左去... 係咪長糧應該放少啲等佢夜晚食多啲罐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"其實有可能係佢唔鍾意食個個罐<br />\n<br />\n你試下放假個陣觀察一下佢<br />\n睇下佢夜晚個餐係幾點食<br />\n係佢一食你就開罐 睇下佢食唔食<br />\n咁就可以試到係飽定唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a447482241f2b5b0a13a4c4414323ff805a698","tid":522544,"uid":64930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"你地放長糧唔會變肥貓咩？同埋唔會食到破產咩？<br />\n我果隻貓女黎，8個月放長糧，未到天黑都已經可以一日食我200g糧仔，唔好話我荷包出血，都驚佢痴肥要慢慢控制返一日60g<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋每次一加落即掃清，到而家都係黑洞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88baa3195e8aab39d13206b5ceed10dd3d4952d","tid":522544,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a447482241f2b5b0a13a4c4414323ff805a698","tid":522544,"uid":64930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"你地放長糧唔會變肥貓咩？同埋唔會食到破產咩？<br />\n我果隻貓女黎，8個月放長糧，未到天黑都已經可以一日食我200g糧仔，唔好話我荷包出血，都驚佢痴肥要慢慢控制返一日60g<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋每次一加落即掃清，到而家都係黑洞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"咁好胃口嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻以前完唔唔like食乾糧，好辛苦先訓練到佢接受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果要出街放長糧就計番你幾點會返，中間要佢自己食幾多餐個份量。返到來都係逐餐胃，因為覺得放長糧會令到隻嘢唔惜食同埋唔衛生。"},{"pid":"39ff5227e9b374683ea076d8ab672c377d951493","tid":522544,"uid":64930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88baa3195e8aab39d13206b5ceed10dd3d4952d","tid":522544,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a447482241f2b5b0a13a4c4414323ff805a698","tid":522544,"uid":64930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"你地放長糧唔會變肥貓咩？同埋唔會食到破產咩？<br />\n我果隻貓女黎，8個月放長糧，未到天黑都已經可以一日食我200g糧仔，唔好話我荷包出血，都驚佢痴肥要慢慢控制返一日60g<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋每次一加落即掃清，到而家都係黑洞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"咁好胃口嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻以前完唔唔like食乾糧，好辛苦先訓練到佢接受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果要出街放長糧就計番你幾點會返，中間要佢自己食幾多餐個份量。返到來都係逐餐胃，因為覺得放長糧會令到隻嘢唔惜食同埋唔衛生。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"如果有貓界放題大賽，我相信佢實win硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食得多時屙得多，放長糧一日屙幾轉，下下都屙成座山出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家都係一日屙兩鑊....<br />\n<br />\n養佢一隻等於兩隻份量既糧砂<br />\n利申：挪威森林貓"},{"pid":"cf2aa9f244989fc562d4cd86792908f7543eae7c","tid":522544,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:17:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36eb059369027ce861c83de4429f1e7c737fc941","tid":522544,"uid":121496,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"貓貓狗狗 ，幾廿歲人重用疊字，知唔知醜字點寫。"},{"pid":"137ae04960ff5fb6ac44878bb4e767e2d6412c60","tid":522544,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"dafa1eec0733738cb78dc8954e459fb7b1bfe74f","tid":522544,"uid":153173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"我歲幾大貓仔 <br />\n一日餵四餐 每餐10幾-20g <br />\n想佢無肥得咁勁 最好少食多餐"}]}